OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGeorge Alagiah takes TV    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbreak after cancer spreads 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC presenter George Alagiah will be   
OL,6, taking a break from TV after           
OL,7, discovering his cancer has spread      
OL,8, further, his agent has said.           
OL,10,FHe was first diagnosed with stage four 
OL,11,Fbowel cancer in 2014 and has stepped   
OL,12,Fback from presenting intermittently for
OL,13,Ftreatment since then.                  
OL,15,FThe journalist, 66, returned to the    
OL,16,FBBC's News at Six in April.            
OL,18,FWorking in the newsroom "has been such 
OL,19,Fan important part of keeping energised 
OL,20,Fand motivated", said Alagiah.          
